.DT
add_enchant
Disk World creator help
add_enchant

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
add_enchant -  Adds number to the current enchantment level of the room.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
int add_enchant(int number)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^number%^RESET%^ - the new enchantment level to set
.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/std/room/basic_room.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

Adds number to the current enchantment level of the room.
The enchanment level controls things like what happens when you
flip coins and some special messages which give wizards some 
idea about magic levels.
.EP

.SH See also
.SP 5 5
query_enchant()

.EP

